 v\u00e6re p\u00e5 siten n\u00e5r det peaker\u00bb", "Thomas Hammeren sier han \u00f8nsker at det ble bygd ei kai, slik at b\u00e5ter kan legge til. Trekaia fra krigens er for lengst r\u00e5tnet opp."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|nyheter"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "dce8b34e03c1654d16312d3ae8ab369b7424a4d54a14f54c9538daec63fa7c30"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-06-27T13:49:38.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Serveringsstedet Ladekaia er blitt en kjempesuksess. Stedet har hatt mer bes\u00f8k enn driverne i sine villeste fantasier kunne forestille seg."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/nyheter/article12931264.ece/av4sr5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/JPS_ladekaia112.JPG"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/08d0f5b548829320fd82c8e2b010fff7b5a0b2e6.jpg?599a1008"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Ladekaia en knallsuksess -adressa.no", "Lange k\u00f8er", "Ammunisjonsskur fra krigen", "Kommunen har bist\u00e5tt", "Satser p\u00e5 gjenbruk", "Plass til 250 gjester", "Sponhuset i Ringvebukta"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "08d0f5b548829320fd82c8e2b010fff7b5a0b2e6"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Ladestien", "Djupvika", "\u00d8stmarkneset", "NGU"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Ladestien,Djupvika,\u00d8stmarkneset,NGU"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "nyheter"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "business"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": ["lade", "burger king"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["hammer", "daglig leder", "sted"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["norges", "sponhuset", "ladekaia", "djupvika", "ringvebukta", "\u00f8stmarkneset", "ladestien"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["r\u00f8ros", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "valu